 <title>Client Migration</title>

 <info>
  <abstract>
   <para>
    &susemgr; supports you with upgrading SLE clients to the latest
    version or SP (service pack).  Upgrading from SLE 12 to SLE 12 SP2
    or later (when available) it straight forward; upgrading form SLE 11
    SPx requires some additional steps, but can be automated.
   </para>
<!--
   <para>
